title: View your vehicle operator safety and risk reports

heading_context: View your vehicle operator safety and risk reports
chunks.html_content:
If you’re a vehicle operator, use this service to:

  • check your latest Operator Compliance Risk Score (OCRS)
  • monitor the MOT pass rates of your vehicles
  • identify causes of vehicle test failures
  • view information about when your drivers or vehicles are checked by a Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) examiner

You need your Vehicle Operator Licensing account username and password if you’ve used the service before.

You can register in the service if you’ve not used it before.

Contact DVSA if you have any questions about how to apply.
